"{\"uid\": \"americansongwriter.com-celine-dion-returns-with-emotional-la-vie-en-rose-performance-while-lady-gaga-sang-in-french-at-olympic-opening-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By  Lauren Boisvert  Updated:  The Olympic Games Opening Ceremony began tonight at 7:30 p.m. Paris time, broadcasting at 1:30 p.m.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET in the U.S., and everything kicked off with Snoop Dogg carrying the Olympic Torch earlier today.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tonight, though,Celine Diontook to the Eiffel Tower to give a gorgeous, emotional performance.\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the day, Lady Gaga performed alongside dancers and a full jazz band on elaborate golden stairs.\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She sang convincingly in French, and later wore a giant fan of white feathers to match the pink feathers the dancers carried.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9639367813965227, \"rank\": 0.034904298484942656, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Kelly Clarkson, who was hosting the ceremony on NBC along with Peyton Manning, shared that Gaga had \\\"no rehearsal.\\\"\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999998113858233, \"rank\": 1.4915599609400745e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peyton Manning\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\"}, {\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.892665042328463e-37, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perched upon the Eiffel Tower in a sparkling white dress, Celine Dion gave a powerful, evocative performance in French accompanied by piano.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.801197944373292e-47, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}, {\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9639367813965227, \"rank\": 0.034904298484942656, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She sang beautifully despite the issues she's been having with her health.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion has been waging a battle against a rare neurological disorder, which she shared with her fans in 2022.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her new documentary,I Am: Celine Dion, gave viewers a unique look into how Stiff Person Syndrome affects her life and career, from the not-so-pretty aspects of it to the debilitating spasms she experiences.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Dion has not let her disease get the better of her, and has been using her resources to invest in therapies and treatments, determined to return to the stage.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the first time she has performed since 2020, when the pandemic forced her to pause her tour.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She then canceled the rest of the tour dates after her diagnosis in March 2022.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[RELATED: Celine Dion in Talks for Las Vegas Residency While Olympics Rumors Swirl: \\\"It's Basically a Done Deal\\\"]  Additionally, Dion has enjoyed being in Paris for the ceremony, as she has shared photos and comments on social media praising the city's beauty.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.488852594604927e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every time I return to Paris, I remember there is so much beauty and joy still to experience in the world.\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1859, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.488852594604927e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love Paris, and I am so happy to be back!\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1943, \"end\": 1955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/I_Love_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"I love Paris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/I_Love_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/I_Love_Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"she wrote on Twitter on Wednesday, July 24.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.925243613781527e-20, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lady Gaga was also seen practicing for the ceremony in Paris, most notablyon a piano which was floating on a platform in the River Seine.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.488852594604927e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Celine Dion, she spoke withVanity Fairat the premiere of her documentary last month about her health and her determination to return to the stage.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When life imposes something on you, you have two options: You deal with it, or you do not,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to deal with it because I am a mother \\u2026 And that is what keeps me positive.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to manage it and tell myself that.\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are moments that are hard.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have days that are better than others.\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not going away.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to deal with this, and I am.\\\"\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She then added resolutely, \\\"I will sing again, that's for sure.\\\"\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured Image by Larry Marano/Shutterstock  Only members can comment.Become a member.Already a member?Log in.\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2778, \"end\": 2784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marano